Revision history for Perl extension Calendar::Simple.

2003-05-14 22:16  dave

	* Simple.pm (1.8): Added support for DateTime.pm (but only if it's
	installed).

2003-02-19 20:17  dave

	* Simple.pm (1.7): Ensure that all week arrays contain seven
	elements - previously the last one ended on the last day of the
	month.

